<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">AD is one of the few factions in WoW that earn you reputation the old EQ way (very slight increase per mob killed).  That said, the primary means is by collecting and turning in batches of scourgestones (dropped by undead minions of the scourge in eastern/western plaguelands and the Stratholme and Scholomance instances).
<br />

<br />
From what I can tell, rep with AD let's you buy high hp/mana food and nothing more.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
