<span class="postbody">Friendly = able to buy manna biscuits (food that gives back HPs and Mana, expensive little shits)
<br />

<br />
Honored = Transmute Air to Fire or some stupid transmute becomes available
<br />

<br />
Revered = Major mana and Major Health potions are now available for buy, 39s a piece
<br />

<br />
Exaulted = supposedly purple armor sets now become available....
<br />

<br />
give me another week or so and ill be able to tell you whats in exaulted faction =)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
