<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">wrong, killing stops giving faction at revered
<br />

<br />
halfway through friendly, lower lvl mobs stop giving faction
<br />

<br />
at the start of honored, mid lvl stuff stops giving faction
<br />

<br />
at about a 1/4-1/2 through honored, high lvl stuff stops giving faction
<br />

<br />
the last half of honored you need bosses / scourgestone / quest to raise faction.
<br />

<br />
at the start of revered, you need to turn in invader+ stones for faction
<br />

<br />
and finally halfway through revered you can only gain faction by turning in corruptor stones.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
